SOUTHWEST AIR CUTS FARES TO MARK NEW ROUTE . Southwest Airlines Co said Tuesday it set $ 99 one - way fares for travel between Albuquerque , N . M . , and Tampa Bay or Orlando , Fla . , to mark the carrier ' s new nonstop service between them . The new nonstop service begins September 7 . The special $ 99 one - way fare must be purchased within one day of making reservations and by September 6 . The fare is valid only on nonstop flights between the markets and is good through November 20 . No stayover is required , Southwest Airline said in a news release . 
